            "value": "60",
            "description": "Studies conducted in early 2026 showed that agents processing HTML pages consumed between 40-60%\nof their token budget on structural noise unrelated to content. JavaScript bundles, CSS class names,\nna",
            "confidence": 0.7
          },
          {
            "@type": "spark:Statistic",
            "value": "47",
