            "confidence": 0.7
          },
          {
            "@type": "spark:Statistic",
            "value": "40",
            "description": "The case for structured protocols is not primarily technical — it is economic. AI companies\ncurrently train models on web content without compensating publishers. The zero-click economy\nhas already de",
            "confidence": 0.7
          },
          {
