            "value": "73",
            "description": "A reduction of 73% in agent preprocessing steps when consuming structured files versus raw HTML\nwas measured in controlled benchmarks. Intent resolution — the process of an agent figuring out\nwhat a b",
            "confidence": 0.7
          },
          {
